songs.title: Uncensored
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
So uncensored
I'm a walking contradiction
My ambitions, my addiction
It turns me on (Oh)
Every day's a reinvention
Faking all the misconceptions, I prove 'em wrong
I get caught in the adrenaline rush, get off
I'm just not givin' up

[Chorus]
Unfiltered, unglued
Yeah, I'm so uncensored
Oh oh, oh oh, oh, oh (Oh, oh)
I'm right on target, just left to center
Oh oh, oh oh, oh, oh (Oh, oh)

[Verse 2]
What's the point of boundaries?
Who makes the rules up, anyways? (Yeah, who?)
'Cause I break 'em all
My scares are deep from memories
But I don't let them get to me, I just move on
I say (I say) whatever comes to my mind, I do (I do)
What feels good at the time

[Chorus]
Unfiltered, unglued
Yeah, I'm so uncensored
Oh oh, oh oh, oh, oh (oh, oh)
I'm right on target, just left to center
Oh oh, oh oh, oh, oh (oh, oh)

[Bridge]
I'm not sorry, why should I be?
It's so awesome to be me
I'm just doing my, m-my thing
Uh uh, uh uh

[Chorus]
Unfiltered, unglued
Yeah, I'm so uncensored
Oh oh, oh oh, oh, oh (Oh, oh)
I'm right on target, just left to center
Oh oh, oh oh, oh, oh (Oh, oh)
Unfiltered, unglued
Yeah, I'm so uncensored
Oh oh, oh oh, oh, oh (Oh, oh)
I'm right on target, just left to center
Oh oh, oh oh, oh, oh (Oh, oh)
